<subSubSection pageNumber="354" type="discussion">
<paragraph pageNumber="354">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="354">Note:</emphasis>
See extensive discussion by Uotila, who rejects 14.3 and 14.4 (LINN) as original material on the grounds that they conflict with the protologue, and designates a 
<typeStatus>neotype</typeStatus>
. This removes the possibility that the name might be a synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="L." authorityName="Linnaeus" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Chenopodium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rubrum">
