L.
</taxonomicName>
, which had led some authors to informally reject 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="354">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1771" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Blitum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="chenopodioides">B. chenopodioides</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
